Package org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.sstation

Class FunctionAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.SclElementAdapter<BayAdapter,​TFunction>
      • org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.sstation.FunctionAdapter
  • public class FunctionAdapter
extends SclElementAdapter<BayAdapter,​TFunction>
    A representation of the model object FunctionAdapter.

    The following features are supported:

    1. Principal functions
      • Add TPrivate under this object
      • Returns the XPATH for this object
      • Add TCompasICDHeader Private in each TLNode reference object
      • Update the value of LNode@iedName attribute corresponding to the value of ICDHeader@IEDName attribute
      • Update the value of LNode@iedName attribute

    XPATH Example : 

               Function[@name="functionName"]

    See Also:
    TLNode, TCompasICDHeader, Issue !124 (update LNode iedName)

      • updateLNodeIedNames

        public void updateLNodeIedNames()
                         throws ScdException
        Updates LNode IED name in current Function
        • If LNode contents one Private Compas-ICDHEADER so LNode name is update with IED name from the Private
        • If LNode contents more than one Private Compas-ICDHEADER so new LNodes are created for each Private Compas-ICDHEADER and naming them with the Private IED name
        Throws:
        ScdException - throws when no Private Compas-ICDHEADER found on at least one LNode of current Function
